reviewText: Prompt delivery, quality product as described on website.

I love Ludovico, I've been listening to his music for quiet some years and everytime I listen to a new album I'm more into him than before, I just saw this concert in California las October/2016 and I was so amazed, that's why I wanted to get the dvd asap. It's a great concert, I'm happy I got it!

Wonderful music and concert.  Sound quality is good.  The reason for 4 stars is that the video, towards the end was flashing red for a couple frames which were a bit annoying.  Not enough to not buy it, but just FYI.
